{"tid":2374913,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"想同人一齊討論扭計骰","createTime":"2021-01-21T14:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:14:08.000Z","uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de112a3d59c90ea223ccf3fab602c5e3a3cedc00","tid":2374913,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"大約一年前開始接觸呢樣嘢<br />\n唔係成日掂<br />\n平時得閒冇嘢做先扭下<br />\n玩咗一年之後開始覺得自己一個玩好悶<br />\n所以想同人一齊交流下<br />\n同埋都有啲問題想問下啲玩得叻嘅人<br />\n希望大家如果都有玩扭計骰就入嚟陪下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5492e276c106224840ced9c5d056da862feb144f","tid":2374913,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"問題1：<br />\n我而家嘅扭法係十字底---&gt;F2L---&gt;兩段式OP<br />\n時間一直維持喺30秒左右<br />\n已經幾個月冇進步退步過<br />\n如果想再快啲係咪要轉用CFOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇有經驗嘅巴絲話我知<br />\n你哋用咗幾耐時間記曬OLL同PLL啲公式<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題2：<br />\n我都有玩高階<br />\n一直覺得個單邊反轉公式又長又唔順手<br />\n想問下有冇方法可以由一開始扭嗰陣就避免到單邊反轉嘅情況<br />\n又或者點樣可以令到個公式順手啲扭快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我學嘅單邊反轉公式：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icMXe6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicMXe6k.jpg&h=4fd932df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題3：<br />\n我都有玩異形<br />\n我係跟呢位youtuber學嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/c/1hrBLD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fc%2F1hrBLD&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=c956a764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/1hrBLD</a><br />\n我覺得佢真係教得好過其他youtuber好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係佢淨係教咗啲異形嘅普通解法<br />\n冇教速解同高階異形嘅解法<br />\n我試過搵其他youtuber啲片嚟睇<br />\n但係睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能我蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下大家有冇覺得好嘅youtuber推介<br />\n又或者有冇其他渠道可以學到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題暫時得咁多<br />\n希望有人可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d0bfa90e2bc45c8878f24f58d8679520a7b4dd","tid":2374913,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"想快一定係CFOP然後背晒oll同pll啲公式<br />\n然後花最多時間應該係second layer, 咁就要靠你扭緊同時觀察既能力<br />\n開頭十字就計時之前望個段時間就要望左點扭"},{"pid":"0548608a108c3d9166aa4f2710f857a91c80ec85","tid":2374913,"uid":317502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"ching有冇tg一齊傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317d9e060ff0f5b3d8059813097cf69da3ede488","tid":2374913,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8d0bfa90e2bc45c8878f24f58d8679520a7b4dd","tid":2374913,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"想快一定係CFOP然後背晒oll同pll啲公式<br />\n然後花最多時間應該係second layer, 咁就要靠你扭緊同時觀察既能力<br />\n開頭十字就計時之前望個段時間就要望左點扭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"ching記咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我見到有五十幾條公式有啲卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4cde074fdc0ded48934566f0ba13574e2f59d70","tid":2374913,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0548608a108c3d9166aa4f2710f857a91c80ec85","tid":2374913,"uid":317502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"ching有冇tg一齊傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66344bab8c3bbc711fa47dbbc41d374c939cd703